# Environment variables for TripCanvas (Next.js).
#
# Setup:
# 1. copy this .env.example file to .env.local or .env file
# 2. fill in values. Never commit .env.local or other real secrets.
#
# Docs: https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/configuring/environment-variables

# Human-readable project name (server-side). Used for page metadata when set.
PROJECT_NAME="XXXXX"